text: N-Formylmorpholine is the organic compound with the formula O(C2H4)2NCHO. It is the formamide of morpholine (O(C2H4)2NH). A colorless compound, it is a useful high temperature solvent akin to dimethylformamide. It has been used as a formylating agent. ==References== Category:Formamides Category:Amide solvents Category:Morpholines
title: N-Formylmorpholine
